{"tid":2273414,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人一到咗夜晚就會諗好多野","createTime":"2020-11-05T17:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T17:33:36.000Z","uid":316086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8bcc8d37e223cbad6dae067a3e6e58f0dd7be7ba","tid":2273414,"uid":316086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"明明自己都叫做幸福，有個幾錫我嘅女朋友，又有朋友（雖然好少，但係好過冇）。但係一到夜晚自己一個果陣，就會喺度諗，其實好多野去到最後都係得自己去面對，冇人可以幫你，或者會幫你。<br />\n有時又諗啲朋友會唔會唔係咁鐘意我，因為佢哋有時會串下我咁。有時又諗女朋友會唔會有一日離開我，所以我更加要珍惜宜家嘅時刻。有時又諗自己究竟幾時先會成長，成為自己想成為嘅果個我。"},{"pid":"7f22fb537806bd8c728e7b42b442b9ef8722a35a","tid":2273414,"uid":15940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"簡單啦 咁早啲瞓"},{"pid":"81957c612033c3931f8a5d457b09a62870c24979","tid":2273414,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"早啲瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93fe851f0b1eeee12d9a8a533629297531b4a733","tid":2273414,"uid":369306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:06:58.000Z","msg":"得啦 有女啦"},{"pid":"1daa7a85642bed534601cd86a3f92d755b775c10","tid":2273414,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"威啦威啦<br />\n我都想好似樓主咁幸福　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b511c2436fb6d3a8586c6229310293b5af5b1537","tid":2273414,"uid":316086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1daa7a85642bed534601cd86a3f92d755b775c10","tid":2273414,"uid":118709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"威啦威啦<br />\n我都想好似樓主咁幸福　<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\